## 3. Pre-Deployment Checklist

Complete every item before triggering deployment. Check off items as you go.

### Code & Review
- [ ] All issues in [Release Scope](Release-Scope-{{ milestone_slug }}) are merged to the release branch
- [ ] Release branch has passed all CI/CD pipeline checks (no failing jobs)
- [ ] Code review sign-off received from at least one senior engineer
- [ ] No unresolved merge conflicts on the release branch

### Testing
- [ ] All automated tests pass (unit, integration, e2e)
- [ ] Regression testing completed on staging
- [ ] Performance / load testing completed (if applicable)
- [ ] Security scan completed — no critical/high vulnerabilities

### Configuration & Infrastructure
- [ ] Environment variables and secrets are updated for all target environments
- [ ] Database migrations reviewed and tested on staging
- [ ] Feature flags configured correctly for this release
- [ ] Infrastructure changes (if any) applied and verified
- [ ] Rollback plan reviewed and confirmed ready (see [Rollback Instructions](Rollback-Instructions-{{ milestone_slug }}))

### Comms
- [ ] Stakeholders notified of deployment window
- [ ] Support team briefed on changes in this release
- [ ] Maintenance window scheduled (if required)

